---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import NavBar from "../components/NavBar.astro";
---

<Layout title='FSOpen'>
  <div class='flex flex-col min-h-screen'>
    <main class='bg-secondary-blue text-white min-h-full grow'>
      <header class='bg-primary-blue lg:h-96 h-56 pt-4'>
        <div class='lg:px-32 px-4 h-full'>
          <NavBar />
          <div
            class='flex flex-col h-[75%] transition-all ease-in justify-center'
          >
            <h1 class='md:text-6xl text-2xl font-bold'>FullStack Open</h1>
            <a
              class='text-zinc-400'
              href='https://github.com/WilliamTrodd/fsopenWTD2.0'>GitHub Repo</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div
        class='py-8 lg:px-32 px-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 md:grid-rows-1 grid-cols-1 grid-rows-2 gap-4 items-center'
      >
        <div
          class='flex flex-col h-full w-full whitespace-nowrap bg-tertiary-blue px-6 py-3 rounded-md'
        >
          <h2 class='text-4xl font-bold mb-3'>Tech Used</h2>
          <ul class=''>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>React</li>
            <li>Redux</li>
            <li>React Native</li>
            <li>MaterialUI</li>
            <li>NodeJS</li>
            <li>Express</li>
            <li>MongoDB</li>
            <li>GraphQL</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class='flex flex-col h-full px-6 py-3 bg-tertiary-blue rounded-md'>
          <h2 class='text-4xl font-bold w-fit'>Details</h2>
          <p>
            This self-led course offered by the University of Helsinki gave me
            access to a variety of fullstack development tools and technologies.
            I was able to learn how to use TypeScript, React, Redux, React
            Native, MaterialUI, NodeJS, Express, MongoDB, and GraphQL. While
            completing this course, I implemented these technologies into
            various fullstack applications, viewable in the linked repo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
